    "This method highlights the importance of each word in the context of the entire dataset, thus helping in identifying key features of each product.",
    "• K-Means Clustering: The vectorized text data is then subjected to K-Means clustering.",
    "This unsupervised learning technique groups the products into distinct clusters based on the similarity of their descriptions.",
    "• Cluster Analysis: Each cluster is analyzed to understand the common characteristics of the products within it.",
    "This analysis helps in categorizing products into meaningful groups."
